e Star Award\n| {{NA}}\n| {{won}}\n| <ref>{{Cite news|url=http://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=108&aid=0002631452 |script-title=ko:\uc774\uc131\uacbd\u00b7\uad8c\ud601\uc218\u00b7\ucc28\uc740\uc6b0\u00b7\ud61c\ub9ac, MTN \ubc29\uc1a1\uad11\uace0 \uc2a4\ud0c0\uc0c1..\"\uac10\uc0ac, \uc601\uad11\"(\uc885\ud569)|date=July 20, 2017|website=Star News|language=ko}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[MBC Entertainment Awards]]\n| Rookie Award in Show / Sitcom \u2013 Male\n| ''[[Show! Music Core]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"7\"|2018\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[11th Korea Drama Awards]]\n| Best New Actor\n| rowspan=\"2\"|''[[Gangnam Beauty]]''\n| {{won}}\n| rowspan=\"2\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://entertain.naver.com/now/read?oid=311&aid=0000904519 |script-title=ko:[\uc885\ud569] '2018 KDA' \uc720\ub3d9\uadfc, \ub300\uc0c1 \uc601\uc608\u2026'\uac19\uc774 \uc0b4\ub798\uc694' 4\uad00\uc655 '\ucf8c\uac70'|date=October 2, 2018|website=My Daily|language=ko}}</ref>\n|-\n| Hallyu Star Award\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| 3rd Indonesian Television Awards\n| Special Award \u2013 Person of the Year\n| {{NA}}\n| {{won}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://pekanbaru.tribunnews.com/2018/10/31/indonesian-television-awards-malam-ini-ada-cha-eun-woo-astro-ini-5-fakta-si-face-genius|title=Indonesian Television Awards Malam Ini, Ada Cha Eun Woo ASTRO! Ini 5 Fakta Si Face Genius|date=October 31, 2018|website=Tribun News|language=id}}</ref>\n|-\n| 3rd [[Asia Artist Awards]]\n| Rising Star Award\n| rowspan=\"3\"|''[[Gangnam Beauty]]''\n| {{won}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://metro.co.uk/2018/11/28/bts-win-the-daesang-at-asia-artist-awards-2018-and-are-among-artists-of-the-year-8187121/|title=BTS win the Daesang at Asia Artist Awards 2018 \u2013 and are among Artists Of The Year|date=November 28, 2018|website=Metro}}</ref>\n|-\n| Yahoo Asia Buzz Awards\n| Most Searched Rookie Actor\n| {{won}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=076&aid=0003357298 |script-title=ko:[\uacf5\uc2dd]\ucc28\uc740\uc6b0, \uc57c\ud6c4 \uc