, Minho, Cha Eun-woo to host MBC\u2019s 2018 Gayo Daejejeon|date=December 17, 2018|website=Kpop Herald}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2019\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://entertain.naver.com//read?oid=241&aid=0002983001|title=\uc724\uc544X\ucc28\uc740\uc6b0, MBC '2019 \uac00\uc694\ub300\uc81c\uc804' MC\u2026\uc5bc\uad74\ucc9c\uc7ac \uc870\ud569|date=November 26, 2019|website=NAVER TV}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n== Awards and nominations ==\n{{Main|List of awards and nominations received by Astro}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+\n! Year\n! Award\n! Category\n! Nominated work\n! Result\n! Ref.\n|-\n| 2016\n| [[MBC Entertainment Awards]]\n| Rookie Award in Music / Talk Show \u2013 Male\n| ''[[Show! Music Core]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|2017\n| 9th MTN Broadcast Advertising Festival\n| CF Male Star Award\n| {{NA}}\n| {{won}}\n| <ref>{{Cite news|url=http://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=108&aid=0002631452 |script-title=ko:\uc774\uc131\uacbd\u00b7\uad8c\ud601\uc218\u00b7\ucc28\uc740\uc6b0\u00b7\ud61c\ub9ac, MTN \ubc29\uc1a1\uad11\uace0 \uc2a4\ud0c0\uc0c1..\"\uac10\uc0ac, \uc601\uad11\"(\uc885\ud569)|date=July 20, 2017|website=Star News|language=ko}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[MBC Entertainment Awards]]\n| Rookie Award in Show / Sitcom \u2013 Male\n| ''[[Show! Music Core]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"7\"|2018\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[11th Korea Drama Awards]]\n| Best New Actor\n| rowspan=\"2\"|''[[Gangnam Beauty]]''\n| {{won}}\n| rowspan=\"2\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://entertain.naver.com/now/read?oid=311&aid=0000904519 |script-title=ko:[\uc885\ud569] '2018 KDA' \uc720\ub3d9\uadfc, \ub300\uc0c1 \uc601\uc608\u2026'\uac19\uc774 \uc0b4\ub798\uc694' 4\uad00\uc655 '\ucf8c\uac70'|date=October 2, 2018|website=My Daily|language=ko}}</ref>\n|-\n| Hallyu Star Award\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| 3rd Indonesian Television Awards\n| Special Award \u2013 Person of the Year\n| {{NA}}\n| {{won}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://pekanbaru.tribunnews.com/2018/10/31/indonesian-television-awards-malam-ini-ada-cha-eun-woo-astro-ini-5-fakt